        },
        {
          "title": "The Secret Agent",
          "year": 2025,
          "note": "Wagner Moura pitched as this year's Fernanda Torres, the international lead the race keeps underrating. Sean's pick to win Best Actor."
        },
        {
          "title": "Blue Moon",
          "year": 2025,
          "note": "Ethan Hawke, boosted by critics into a likely nomination after George Clooney faded. A snub still wouldn't shock them, given how the two Linklater films split attention."
